Package: fastqnsn
Type: Package
Title: Fast and Optimized Qn and Sn Robust Scale Estimators
Version: 1.0.4
Authors@R: 
    person("Dennis Alexis Valin", "Dittrich",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "davd@economicscience.net",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4438-8276"))
Description: High-performance, multi-threaded implementation of Rousseeuw-Croux
    Qn and Sn robust scale estimators. Re-engineered utilizing C++ arena memory
    allocation, Floyd-Rivest subset selection, and explicit 64-bit boundaries to
    resolve legacy integer overflows. Safely calculates exact scales on massive 
    Big Data sequences up to N=10^8 on standard architectures while delivering a 
    consistent 5x to 15x real-world speedup over legacy implementations.
